Package org.team.pada.unibook.data

Class Person

java.lang.Object
org.team.pada.unibook.data.Person
Direct Known Subclasses:
Professor, Student
public class Person extends Object
Represents a person with a first name, last name, phone number, and email address. This class serves as a base class for other entities such as students or professors.
